> Astrotrain's speakers crackle to life, "Alright. We're heading back 
> to base, correct Cyclonus?" His hatch closes, and he lifts off the 
> ground, into the air and hovers about 20 feet above the ground, his 
> vertical thrusters keeping him stable in mid air.


::Domnijoe::

   Domnijoe grunted.
   "He said something about going back to base before taking off."
she 
said.
   Her engines roared as she launched herself into the sky. She 
circled Astrotain widely from the air. 
   "So which direction?" she asked.
